(67, 1, '2018-12-08 11:07:32', '2018-12-08 16:07:32', '<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Here are some cool things I have created.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Communication Design – Interactive Media program at North Island College keeps me extremely busy building real world projects with the latest tools in Design and Software Development. Below are a few of my favourites.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":293,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Tea_Centre_iPad-1024x725.png\" alt=\"Image of Tea Centre website in iPad.\" class=\"wp-image-293\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"project-title\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"project-title\">Tea Centre, Courtenay</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"project-sub-title\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"project-sub-title\">Website re-design.</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I built the entire site using only HTML, CSS and JavaScript. I used a small amount of jQuery, most of it I built using vanilla JS. I also utilized leaflet to embed a location map and custom wrote a form validation script.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":302} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Super_text_web_mobile-1024x447.png\" alt=\"Image of super-text web and mobile site.\" class=\"wp-image-302\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"project-title\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"project-title\">Super Text, Typography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"project-sub-title\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"project-sub-title\">Web and Mobile mockup in Adobe Illustrator.</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This project required me to build a mock desktop and mobile website based off of a poster that I initially created. The main focus was on the typographic concepts of hierarchy and alignment but also an overarching emphasis on website design and best practices (ie mobile first design).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":319} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/I_and_Eye_Web_iPad.png\" alt=\"I and Eye Magazine image.\" class=\"wp-image-319\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"project-title\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"project-title\">I &amp; Eye Magazine</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"className\":\"project-sub-title\"} -->\n<h4 class=\"project-sub-title\">An Online Magazine built with Wordpress.</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As part of our Content Management Systems course we had a web design contest for I &amp; Eye Magazine, an online publication produced by the students at NIC. I was lucky enough to create the winning design that is currently being used by the Magazine :) . You can view it <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Drumroll please... And the winner of the I &amp; Eye online magazine re-design contest is none other than yours truly :) As part of our Content Management Systems course we had a web design contest for I &amp; Eye Magazine, an online publication produced by the students at NIC. The winning design is currently being used by the Magazine. You can view it here. (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://iandeyemagazine.ca/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->', 'Projects', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'projects', '', '', '2018-12-09 21:28:05', '2018-12-10 02:28:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=67', 0, 'page', '', 0),
