(324, 1, '2018-12-09 18:04:10', '2018-12-09 23:04:10', '<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":273,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":175,\"height\":175} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/jason-portrait.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-273\" width=\"175\" height=\"175\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Hey</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"hello-text\"} -->\n<p class=\"hello-text\">I am a student in the Communication Design - Interactive Media program at North Island College. I have a passion for designing and developing for the web.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>What I can help you with.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":25} -->\n<div style=\"height:25px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":268,\"width\":250,\"height\":250,\"className\":\"web-tools\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized web-tools\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Web_Tools.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-268\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Making the Web Look Awesome.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My favourite tools are HTML, CSS and Javascript. I focus on a clean, simple design that will effectively deliver your message.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":25} -->\n<div style=\"height:25px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Digital Media Creation.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My second favourite tools are Illustrator, Photoshop and Indesign. I am very comfortable working with \"The Big 3\" in Adobe\'s Design Suite.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":270,\"width\":250,\"height\":250,\"className\":\"adobe-tools\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized adobe-tools\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Digital_Tools.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-270\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Let\'s do this.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>I\'m available, reasonable and available.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are in need of a creative, detail oriented web designer to help you with your next project. Or if you like what you see but just want to get a coffee...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":10} -->\n<div style=\"height:10px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:button {\"customBackgroundColor\":\"#6e7da2\",\"customTextColor\":\"#fcf8f3\",\"className\":\"is-style-squared\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-squared\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background\" href=\"mailto:tompeij@gmail.com\" style=\"background-color:#6e7da2;color:#fcf8f3\"><strong>✉</strong> DROP ME A MAIL</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->', 'I\'m Jason,', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '64-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-09 18:04:10', '2018-12-09 23:04:10', '', 64, 'http://localhost:8888/64-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(325, 1, '2018-12-09 18:26:42', '2018-12-09 23:26:42', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>And this is where I rant about how hard this project <del>was</del>&nbsp;is! Believe me when I say this...&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://render.bitstrips.com/v2/cpanel/ef2ea898-c606-49aa-baeb-f882a9f55e21-b5c24c80-49cc-4620-be8a-eaffff75f595-v1.png?transparent=1&amp;palette=1\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using underscores as my starter theme may have been a bit more challenging than I first considered. I thought, are starter themes really all that difficult to do? With underscores (or is it _s?) you really are just getting a blank slate. No fanciness included. Just you and Wordpress.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":350} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/underscores.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-350\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is literally what my website looked like when I started. (well not literally because I forgot to take a screenshot before I styled it so I found this on sitepoint, thanks sitepoint) So yeah, I spent most of my time with style.css open and frantically trying to find classes to hook onto so I could add some life to my site. I learned a ton of new things, like how much better Gutenberg is compared to the old WP editor. I also got real familiar with the page hierarchy and I feel like I can navigate through all these php files a little better than when I started. I still have a long way to go before I would consider myself any kind of authority so thank god we have the \"Show Current Template\" plugin!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At the end of <del>the day</del> 3 days I have started something here and I plan to keep refining it and correcting the inevitable mistakes that I have, and will probably continue to make. Kudos underscores team (or however you want to be called) you forced me to stop reverting to big fancy themes and Elementor :D</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->', 'Dear _s:', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'my-only-entry', '', '', '2018-12-10 11:02:30', '2018-12-10 16:02:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=325', 0, 'post', '', 0),
